---
title: Easy Breezy Grilling Cheesy with Lemony Couscous, Grape Tomatoes & Kale
description: In the HF Kitchen, we’re pretty obsessed with grilling cheese—it has the ultimate ability to fry on the outside, and get all melty on the inside. For tonight’s edition of the Grilling Cheese Fan Club, we’re coating the cheese in Italian spices before pan-searing. On the side, you’ll make a lemony couscous with sautéed kale and grape tomatoes. Get ready for one beautiful and delicious veg-masterpiece.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/easy-breezy-grilling-cheesy-2b962330.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/easy-breezy-grilling-cheesy-615db95e0ab39518157b909b-564744e7.pdf
author: Michelle Doll Olson
servings: 2
course: main course
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/easy-breezy-grilling-cheesy-615db95e0ab39518157b909b
cuisine: Italian
nutrition:
  calories: 770 kcal
